          </div>
        </a>
        <p class="book__trademark">
          Amazon's trademark is used under license from Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="book__description animate-in">
        <p>
          Questo libro porta il lettore dal concetto di <strong>grafo di conoscenza</strong> fino a un
          sistema funzionante in produzione, capace di rispondere a domande in linguaggio naturale su
          documenti aziendali.
        </p>
        <p>
          Copre l'intero ciclo: modelli dati, ontologie, pipeline RAG, Vector Store,
          LLM, <strong>Model Context Protocol</strong> e orchestrazione <strong>multi-agente</strong>
          con Microsoft Agent Framework.
        </p>
        <p>
          Pensato per <strong>sviluppatori Python</strong>, data engineer e AI engineer che vogliono
          costruire un KG reale, ma anche per <strong>CTO e product manager</strong> che vogliono
          valutare il potenziale dei Knowledge Graph e stimare il ROI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Formats -->
      <div class="book__formats animate-in">
        <h3 class="book__section-title">Formati disponibili</h3>
        <div class="formats-row">
          {formats.map((fmt) => (
            <div class="format-item">
              <span class="format-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">{fmt.icon}</span>
              <span class="format-item__label">{fmt.label}</span>
              <span class="format-item__detail">{fmt.detail}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="book__parts animate-in">
        <h3 class="book__section-title">Struttura del libro</h3>
        <div class="parts-grid">
          {parts.map((part) => (
            <div class="part-item">
              <span class="part-item__number">Parte {part.number}</span>
              <span class="part-item__title">{part.title}</span>
              <span class="part-item__chapters">Cap. {part.chapters}</span>
              <span class="part-item__desc">{part.desc}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="book__stack animate-in">
        <h3 class="book__section-title">Stack tecnologico</h3>
        <div class="stack-tags">
          {stack.map((tech) => (
            <span class="stack-tag">{tech}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .book {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .book__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .book__badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.2em 0.8em;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-bg);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .book__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .book__subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.1rem);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-sm);
  }

  .book__meta {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .book__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  /* ── Amazon CTA Button ── */
  .book__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .book__buy-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-xl);
    background: #ff9900;
    color: #111;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      transform var(--transition-base),
      box-shadow var(--transition-base),
      background var(--transition-base);
  }

  .book__buy-btn:hover {
    background: #ffad33;
    color: #111;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 153, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .book__amazon-logo {
    width: 80px;
    height: auto;
    color: #111;
  }

  .book__buy-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .book__buy-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .book__buy-formats {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* ── Available at Amazon Badge (KDP compliant) ── */
  .book__amazon-badge {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .amazon-badge-link {
    display: inline-block;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .amazon-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    background: #232f3e;
    border-radius: 8px;
    min-width: 140px;
  }

  .amazon-badge__text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .amazon-badge__logo {
    width: 100px;
    height: auto;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .book__trademark {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* ── Description ── */
  .book__description p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .book__description p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .book__description strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .book__section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* ── Formats ── */
  .formats-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .format-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-base);
  }

  .format-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .format-item__icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .format-item__label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .format-item__detail {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* ── Parts grid ── */
  .parts-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .part-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 0 var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    transition:
      border-color var(--transition-base),
      box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .part-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--color-accent-glow);
  }

  .part-item__number {
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
    align-self: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .part-item__title {
